<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta
      name="viewport"
      content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no"
    />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no" />
    <link rel="icon" href="data:;base64,=" />
    <script src="./flexible-custom.js"></script>
    <title>订正功能说明</title>
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 0.30667rem 0.2667rem; /*20px;*/
        height: 100%;
        font-size: 14px;
        background-color: #f4f5f7;
      }
      .column {
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 0.306667rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background-color: #fff;
      }
      .bg-color {
        background-color: #fbfbfc;
      }
      .header {
        margin-top: 0.77333rem;
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .header-num {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-right: 5px;
        height: 23px;
        line-height: 23px;
        width: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 17px;
        color: #fff;
        border-top-right-radius: 45%;
        border-bottom-right-radius: 45%;
        background-color: #16cac2;
      }
      .header-txt {
        color: #404040;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .title {
        /* 89px */
        position: relative;
        padding: 25px 42px 0 42px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      .title-icon {
        display: inline-block;
        position: absolute;
        top: 33px;
        background-color: #fff;
        width: 5px;
        height: 5px;
        margin: 0;
        border-radius: 50%;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px #ffba27;
      }
      .title-txt {
        /* display: inline-block; */
        margin-left: 12px;
        color: #57595b;
      }
      .detail {
        padding: 0.2667rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .detail img {
        width: 100%;
      }
      .divide {
        margin: 0 auto;
        height: 1px;
        width: 82%;
        background-color: #f3f3f5;
        /* background-color: red; */
      }
      .circle {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.333333rem;
        right: 1.333333rem;
        width: 10px;
        height: 10px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background-color: #eafdfb;
      }
      .circle-right {
        position: absolute;
        top: 0.333333rem;
        right: 0;
        width: 0.9rem;
        height: 1.8rem;
        border-radius: 0.9rem 0 0 0.9rem; /* 左上、右上、右下、左下 */
        background-color: #f9fefd;
      }
      .circle-top {
        position: absolute;
        right: 0.3rem;
        width: 1.4rem;
        height: 0.7rem;
        border-radius: 0 0 0.7rem 0.7rem; /* 左上、右上、右下、左下 */
        background-color: #fefaf3;
      }
      .circle-top-big {
        position: absolute;
        right: 0.3rem;
        width: 1.8rem;
        height: 0.9rem;
        border-radius: 0 0 0.9rem 0.9rem; /* 左上、右上、右下、左下 */
        background-color: #f8fdfd;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="column bg-white">
        <div class="circle"></div>
        <div class="circle-right"></div>
        <div class="header">
          <span class="header-num">1</span>
          <span class="header-txt">开启订正开关</span>
        </div>
        <div class="title">
          <div><span class="title-icon" style="line-height: 50px;"></span></div>
          <div class="title-txt">发布练习时开启订正开关</div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail"><img src="./img/dingzheng.png" alt="订正" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="column bg-color">
        <div class="circle-top"></div>
        <div class="header">
          <span class="header-num">2</span>
          <span class="header-txt">学生可收到订正练习</span>
        </div>
        <div class="title">
          <div><span class="title-icon"></span></div>
          <div class="title-txt">
            学生提交练习后，被批改完成的练习中，未得满分的练习将被打回订正，学生完成订正练习后才可查看报告。
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail"><img src="./img/liebiao.png" alt="列表" /></div>

        <div class="divide"></div>

        <div class="title">
          <div><span class="title-icon"></span></div>
          <div class="title-txt">
            批改完成后，学生端练习自动重置为一份订正练习，学生需要订正所有未达满分的错题。
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail"><img src="./img/datika.png" alt="答题卡" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="column bg-white">
        <div class="circle"></div>
        <div class="circle-top-big"></div>
        <div class="header">
          <span class="header-num">3</span>
          <span class="header-txt">练习报告中查看订正进度</span>
        </div>
        <div class="title">
          <div><span class="title-icon"></span></div>
          <div class="title-txt">
            学生订正提交后，老师可以在练习报告中查看学生的订正情况。
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="detail"><img src="./img/jindu.png" alt="进度" /></div>
      </div>
      <div class="column"></div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
